# Conclusion

This project demonstrates an end-to-end data warehousing solution using DuckDB and SQL. It showcases how raw operational data can be transformed into business-ready analytical models that support customer delivery analysis, product performance evaluation, and supply chain decision-making through well-designed dimensional models and data marts.
